Title: [ANN][ICO] Inmediate - The Smart Insurance Platform powered by the Zilliqa
Body: The project will operate on the Zilliqa blockchain, which is designed to be able to scale to thousands of transactions per second and has very extensive smart contract capabilities. The Team behind Inmediate is relatively small, however they have been on the insurance market for some time already and have built a full-service insurance platform that guides customers to help them find and buy insurance that best fits their needs.
